  <aside aria-label="Management suggestions" class="grid__item two-fifths lap-one-third palm-one-whole float--right">
    <p class="islet islet--bordered">The <a href="http://genealogy-quest.com/glossary-terms/latin/">Latin glossary</a> on  <a href="http://genealogy-quest.com/">Genealogy Quest</a> is an excellent additional reference for many of the less commonly used terms. We advise you to bookmark the glossary for later use. It is easy to use and is more accurate than Google translate.</p>
